{
  "id": "where-we-call-home",
  "wiki_path": "/wiki/Where_We_Call_Home",
  "wiki_image_url": "https://ffxiv.consolegameswiki.com/mediawiki/images/c/c3/Where_we_call_home1.png",
  "patch": "7.4",
  "title_en": "Where We Call Home",
  "level": "100",
  "location": "Treno(X:11.8,Y:15.1)",
  "npc_start": "Lumull",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "Cargo Operator",
      "text_en": "I really could have gone without a Doomtrain attack today..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Ready? Then our fearless operator will help you aboard."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "We make for Bentini with all haste!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Go on, climb aboard!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Cargo Operator",
      "text_en": "I'll have us there in a flash! Do keep any limbs you're attached to and would like to remain attached to inside the vehicle."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "This is it."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "You'll be riding that flatcar at the rear of the train."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "I'll be all the way at the front, pushing her as fast as she can go."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "The Doomtrain moves at breakneck speed. If we're too slow, it'll plow right through us."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Speaking of which, we'd best get underway before it does just that..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Don't forget you're fighting for Eyaney. For all of Treno."
    },
    {
      "character": "Cargo Operator",
      "text_en": "Hit by a train in Treno or hit by a train out here, it's all the same to me."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Using our on-board systems, I should be able to monitor you from the locomotive. And you'll be able to hear me!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Here it comes! Brace for impact!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "We're in it now... I'm counting on you!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Waugh, the flatcar!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Turrets!? Uh...good luck!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Not again... You all right back there?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Use the transport panels to get up there!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "How many times is it going to do that!?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "What in the─ You're still on board, right!?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Aetherial...arms...?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "I have to disconnect the car. Quick, jump on the next one!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Thunderous heavens!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Hit it harder!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Phew..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "No more adventures, thank you. That was enough bravery for a lifetime."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "But we did it! We stopped the Doomtrain! Well, mostly you did."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "Before we can celebrate, though, we need to make sure Treno's secure."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "As I feared. Stray beasts to the south."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "I've lost track of how many times I've asked you for help, but...I need your help again."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "I have to believe that Eyaney will be safe with your comrades while we attend to matters elsewhere."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull",
      "text_en": "I'll see to the wounded. You try not to join them, alright?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Imperiled Milalla",
      "text_en": "No!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Can you stand?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Imperiled Milalla",
      "text_en": "Y-Yes! Thank you so much!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Imperiled Milalla",
      "text_en": "There were others being attacked over by the canal. Could you possibly...?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Of course, I'll go right away. The rest of you should get to the town hall."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "I can't leave anyone behind. I won't!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Best make sure the evacuation route is clear first..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Done! Now to aid those people by the canal..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Scared Citizen",
      "text_en": "H-Heeelp!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "Waugh!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "We're trapped!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Storming Thunder Spirit",
      "text_en": "<shriek>"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Help is on the way!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Scared Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "S-Scared? Who, m-m-me?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "My thanks!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "What incredible magic!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "Get to safety!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "There may be other stragglers..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "I was so scared I couldn't even move! Silly, isn't it? Haha...ha...ha..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "My wife and I will be making for town hall straightaway. You have my word on that!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "If you're determined to check on everyone, I won't complain, but do be careful."
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "Come on!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Be careful!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "That breeze is awfully warm... Oh no!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Sorrowful Citizen",
      "text_en": "Our home..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "It's really on fire!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "Aaaaaaah!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "We can't haul enough water for this..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "I noticed! Bring water!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "First things first─the fire!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "To take a leaf out of Y'shtola's book..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Thank you, my friend!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "What sort of magic was that? I've never seen the like!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "...Priorities. Yes. I'm going to run away, and we can talk about it later!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "Let's go!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen 2",
      "text_en": "It was you that put the fire out? How will I ever thank you..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen 2",
      "text_en": "Now that we know it won't be spreading any further, we can all take shelter until this is over."
    },
    {
      "character": "Shocked Citizen",
      "text_en": "I cannot thank you enough!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Not a moment too soon... I hope that was the worst of it."
    },
    {
      "character": "Stressed Citizen",
      "text_en": "Somebody, help!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "A voice...further out!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "Eek!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "I'll take care of this─make for shelter!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "Phew..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "That was close..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Citizen (text bubble)",
      "text_en": "Ack!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "How many are there...?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Is that all of them...?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "A behemoth!?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "We cut that rather close."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Thank goodness you're all right!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Eyaney has finished the repairs. We need only hold the line until the barrier is in place."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "And hold the line we will, together!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "I can still fight! I can!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "I have no doubt!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Spread out!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Oh dear..."
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Get back!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "We must move!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Get clear!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Prepare to move..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Such incredible power..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Run!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Thunderheads..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Keep away from the clouds!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "If I never see another storm..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Nowhere is safe with so many of them..."
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "We need a solution!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Some friendly winds, if you please!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Let us see if we can't get some help..."
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Visions of Haam..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Well done, Krile!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Clever..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "It worked!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "How fortunate that bird made such an impression."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "From above!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Have care!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Again!?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Look for the gaps!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Greater Behemoth",
      "text_en": "Grrroooaaar!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Aaah!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "<grunt>"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Oof!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Ah..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "The levin grows more volatile... Something is coming."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Ball lightning!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Y'shtola, Sphene─lend me your strength!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Of course."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "Understood!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "The two of us will disperse these balls of lightning!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Just keep the lightning at bay a little longer!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Take cover behind the spriggan!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "I believe!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "But will it be enough..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "We are in your debt!"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "Fantastic!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "<huff> ...Ngh..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Impressive."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "The tide is turning. Press the attack!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "[EXHAUSTED SIGH]"
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "I must say, that was an incredible performance."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "Flatterer."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "What is it?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "The barrier is restored. The people of Treno may rest easy once more."
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull (Broadcast)",
      "text_en": "The perimeter is clear, everyone! And thanks to our guests, the Doomtrain has been destroyed!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull (Broadcast)",
      "text_en": "Last but not least, Eyaney's fixed the barrier. We don't need to worry about beasts anymore!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Lumull (Broadcast)",
      "text_en": "This calls for a celebration!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Dauntless Laborer",
      "text_en": "The Doomtrain is gone for good!?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Unnamed Milalla",
      "text_en": "That's our Eyaney!"
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "They're safe... All of them..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "Alayla...?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "Krile, does the name “Alayla” mean aught to you?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "My mother? Did you... Did you know her?"
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "[PAINED NOISE OF FALLING TO KNEES]"
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "I'm sorry, my dear. We should get you patched up before aught else."
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "Alayla's story and that of the key are one and the same. After you've rested and recovered, I'll tell you the tale."
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "You have no cause to fret, I promise you."
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "While Lumull forgot to give the order─bless him─there's work to be done ere we can celebrate."
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "First and foremost, we must see to any injured."
    },
    {
      "character": "Miayli",
      "text_en": "Come and find me at town hall when you're ready."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Without further delay, then..."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "You needn't mind me. My injuries are far from severe."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "But your curiosity is another matter, is it not? Your feet will deliver you to Miayli all the swifter if you can actually walk on them."
    },
    {
      "character": "Y'shtola",
      "text_en": "Exhaustion aside, Krile sustained no injuries you need worry over."
    },
    {
      "character": "G'raha Tia",
      "text_en": "After that battle, I think we all required a moment. You had better get some rest too─I mean it."
    },
    {
      "character": "Sphene",
      "text_en": "To think Miayli knew Krile's mother... I too am eager to hear the details."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "While I would rather not have tumbled to the pavement in front of half the city, I am none the worse for wear, thanks to Y'shtola."
    },
    {
      "character": "Krile",
      "text_en": "But what of yourself? If you have any hurts, we can tend to them now before we see Miayli."
    }
  ]
}